Dialogue: 100,0:00:03.86,0:00:06.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 我已经快猜到这个惊喜是什么了\N{\rENG}I'm starting to guess the surprise, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:06.93,0:00:08.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我跟你说了要闭上眼睛噢\N{\rENG}I told you to close your eyes!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:08.93,0:00:10.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不好意思\N{\rENG}Sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:10.64,0:00:12.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好了 在这等着\N{\rENG}Okay, wait here!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:13.54,0:00:15.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}萨普莱斯!\N{\rENG}Surprise!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:17.74,0:00:19.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们买了一艘船!\N{\rENG}We bought a boat!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:19.11,0:00:22.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 纠正一下 --我们租了一艘船\N{\rENG}Uh, correction --We rented a boat.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:22.11,0:00:24.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我虽然现在是暴富了 但是买一艘船\N{\rENG}I may be rich, but buying a boat would be going
Dialogue: 100,0:00:24.58,0:00:27.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}未免也太过了\N{\rENG}a bit overboard.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.69,0:00:35.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就是一个我从水手们那学的笑话啦\N{\rENG}Just a joke I picked up from some sailors.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.19,0:00:37.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他们的幽默感总是令人惊讶\N{\rENG}They have a surprisingly clean sense of humor.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.96,0:00:39.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 这是谁啊\N{\rENG}Steven,who is this?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:39.46,0:00:41.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 葛雷格·宇宙\N{\rENG}Uh,Greg Universe.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.13,0:00:43.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你曾经弄断我的腿 试着利用海洋\N{\rENG}You broke my leg trying to use the ocean
Dialogue: 100,0:00:43.17,0:00:44.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}飞回你的母星\N{\rENG}to fly back to your homeworld.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:44.94,0:00:48.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这里青金石壁琉璃 很高兴认识你\N{\rENG}Lapis Lazuli. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:50.11,0:00:53.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}很好 那么 我要去启动这艘船了\N{\rENG}Great! Well,I'll get the boat started.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:53.18,0:00:54.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么你觉得怎么样\N{\rENG}So what do you think?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:54.91,0:00:56.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这很好了 史蒂文\N{\rENG}It's nice, Steven...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.82,0:00:57.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是 我不确定自己是怎么考虑的\N{\rENG}but I don't know.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.52,0:01:02.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}青金石 我知道你和铁石英\N{\rENG}Look, Lapis, I know you spent a really long time fused
Dialogue: 100,0:01:02.19,0:01:04.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在海底融合了相当久\N{\rENG}with Jasper at the bottom of the ocean,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.19,0:01:06.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是你现在已经不再是孔雀石了\N{\rENG}but you're not Malachite anymore.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:06.19,0:01:07.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而水是你自身的一部分\N{\rENG}And water is a part of who you are.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:07.23,0:01:11.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你不能因为一次糟糕的经历就放弃这部分\N{\rENG}You can't let one bad experience take that away from you.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.70,0:01:13.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不止一次\N{\rENG}It was more than one.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.33,0:01:13.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就当只是尝试好了\N{\rENG}Just give it a chance.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.80,0:01:17.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我发誓你会感到前所未有的乐趣\N{\rENG}I promise we'll make this the most fun you've ever had.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:17.80,0:01:20.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 我...不配拥有这些\N{\rENG}Steven,I...don't deserve this.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:20.71,0:01:22.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你当然配了!\N{\rENG}Of course you do!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:22.17,0:01:25.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们甚至给这艘船命名为小琉璃号\N{\rENG}We even named her Li'l Lappy.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:29.51,0:01:31.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧 我会尝试一下的\N{\rENG}Okay. I'll give it a chance.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:31.88,0:01:33.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是 就一下\N{\rENG}But, just one.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:37.92,0:01:39.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们两个准备好启程了吗\N{\rENG}You two ready to set sail?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.99,0:01:41.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是的 船长!\N{\rENG}Aye, aye, Captain!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.99,0:01:43.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是的\N{\rENG}Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:45.40,0:01:47.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}全速前进--\N{\rENG}Full speed ahe--
Dialogue: 100,0:01:48.97,0:01:51.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哎呀 你觉得会有人发现吗\N{\rENG}Ah, geez, you think anyone will notice?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:54.04,0:01:55.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔啊 我想我真的重创了那个码头\N{\rENG}Wow, I think I did a number on that dock.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:55.54,0:01:59.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也许其他人应该试试当船长\N{\rENG}Maybe somebody else should take a shot at being captain.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:59.21,0:02:02.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你怎么看 青金石船长?\N{\rENG}What do you say, Captain Lazuli?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:02.38,0:02:03.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不该当\N{\rENG}I shouldn't.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:03.72,0:02:05.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}上嘛 青金石\N{\rENG}Go for it, Lapis.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:05.02,0:02:06.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不要把控制权给我!\N{\rENG}Don't put me in charge!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:06.55,0:02:08.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 对不起\N{\rENG}Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:08.02,0:02:10.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是说 我-我不懂驾船的事\N{\rENG}I mean, y-you shouldn't trust me with the boat.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:10.92,0:02:12.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 没关系 不用困扰\N{\rENG}Uh, that's okay. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:12.12,0:02:15.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们可以都当大副 这样就没有竞争压力了\N{\rENG}We can all be first mates so there's no pressure.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:15.89,0:02:17.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}今天只能用来嗨!\N{\rENG}Only fun stuff today!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:17.86,0:02:20.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}青金石 如果你想的话还是可以戴这顶帽子的\N{\rENG}Lapis, you can still wear the hat, if you want.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:20.90,0:02:23.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谢谢 但是我不想让那东西戴在我身上\N{\rENG}Thanks, but I'm not putting that on my body.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:24.80,0:02:27.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让我们嗨起来 --\N{\rENG}Let's set a course for f-u-u-un!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:05.38,0:03:07.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}老爹 老爹\N{\rENG}Dad! Dad!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:07.11,0:03:10.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 你们俩终于玩腻那个喇叭了?\N{\rENG}Hey, you two. Finally get enough of that horn?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:10.18,0:03:11.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啥\N{\rENG}What?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:12.85,0:03:14.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你在干什么?\N{\rENG}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:14.35,0:03:15.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}钓鱼\N{\rENG}Catching fish.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:16.99,0:03:18.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 我来帮忙\N{\rENG}Oh, I can help!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:23.86,0:03:26.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么鬼?!!?\N{\rENG}What the?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:34.07,0:03:37.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这确实是一种 呃 非常拽的钓鱼法\N{\rENG}That's a pretty uh...fancy way of catching fish.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.98,0:03:41.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那是因为青金石超厉害的!\N{\rENG}That's 'cause Lapis is supa' strong!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:41.05,0:03:43.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我 呃 感谢你的好意\N{\rENG}Well, I, uh, appreciate the gesture,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是我觉得坚持用\N{\rENG}but I-I think it would be safer to stick
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.28,0:03:47.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}传统的方法比较安全\N{\rENG}to the old-fashioned way of doing it.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:47.89,0:03:50.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 呃...当然\N{\rENG}Oh, uh...sure.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:55.46,0:03:58.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哇 青金石 那太了不起了\N{\rENG}Wow, Lapis!That was ama...zing...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.90,0:04:02.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么 你们传统的方法是怎么样的\N{\rENG}So, how do you fish the old-fashioned way?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:02.17,0:04:03.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 非常简单\N{\rENG}Oh, it's pretty simple.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:03.97,0:04:05.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你先准备一根钓鱼竿\N{\rENG}You start with a rod,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:05.20,0:04:07.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在鱼线末端绑上一个钩子\N{\rENG}and you put a hook on the end of your line.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:07.34,0:04:08.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后 当你感觉到鱼咬钩了\N{\rENG}And then,when you feel a nibble,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.87,0:04:10.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你就收线把它拉上来\N{\rENG}you reel it in.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.44,0:04:12.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就这样\N{\rENG}And there it is.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:12.44,0:04:14.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你给自己钓了一条鱼来吃!\N{\rENG}You've caught yourself a fish to eat!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:14.18,0:04:16.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是鱼为什么要咬钩\N{\rENG}But why would a fish ever bite a hook?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.92,0:04:19.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你要放上鱼饵\N{\rENG}You got to bait it --put something on it
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.05,0:04:23.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你知道鱼喜欢什么 像虫子或者20刀的纸币之类的\N{\rENG}you know it wants,like a worm or a $20 bill.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:23.05,0:04:25.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}来 我示范给你看\N{\rENG}Here, I'll show you.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:25.32,0:04:27.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}钓鱼\N{\rENG}Fishing.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.36,0:04:34.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}上钩的那一部分要什么时候开始\N{\rENG}When does the fish part happen?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:34.70,0:04:37.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有些时候 钓鱼的意义不在于渔获多少\N{\rENG}Well, sometimes it isn't about the fish you keep,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:37.24,0:04:39.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而在于你与身边的人共度的好时光\N{\rENG}but the company you catch.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:39.57,0:04:41.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哇 鱼咬钩了!\N{\rENG}Whoa!I got a bite.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}青金石 来试试\N{\rENG}Lapis, here!Give it a try!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:43.98,0:04:46.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就像那样拿着竿然后收线\N{\rENG}Hold it just like that and reel it in slowly.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.91,0:04:50.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}像这样?\N{\rENG}Like this?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:50.05,0:04:52.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}完全没错 看起来是条大鱼!\N{\rENG}You got it. It looks like a big one!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:53.72,0:04:54.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}青金石\N{\rENG}Lapis!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.85,0:04:55.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文\N{\rENG}Steven!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.99,0:04:58.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你能做到的 青金石\N{\rENG}You got it, Lapis!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:58.09,0:04:59.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}把它钓上来\N{\rENG}Reel it in!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.36,0:05:02.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}它...拽的...力气好大!\N{\rENG}It's...pulling...so hard!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看来租鱼竿\N{\rENG}Looks likethis pole rental turned
Dialogue: 100,0:05:16.17,0:05:18.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}得变成买鱼竿了\N{\rENG}into a pole purchase.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:18.01,0:05:21.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是你在与那野兽的斗争中非常给力\N{\rENG}But you did a great job tangling with that beast.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是-是啊\N{\rENG}Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:22.38,0:05:24.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不用为没钓上的那条鱼失落\N{\rENG}Don't worry about that one getting away.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:24.45,0:05:26.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 谢谢你\N{\rENG}Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:26.55,0:05:29.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧 今天我的冒险任务也到上限了\N{\rENG}Welp, that's my adventure quota for the day.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:29.35,0:05:32.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我去驾驶室 有什么事找我就吆喝一声\N{\rENG}I'll be at the controls. Holler if you need me.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.22,0:05:35.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是 长官 青金石 你...\N{\rENG}Yes, sir!Lapis, what do you...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.89,0:05:37.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}青金石?\N{\rENG}Lapis?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:40.76,0:05:43.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 你在干什么呢\N{\rENG}Hey. Whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.20,0:05:45.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我只是觉得我需要坐一会儿\N{\rENG}I just thought I'd sit for a bit.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:45.94,0:05:48.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在鱼竿折断之前 你看起来\N{\rENG}You looked like a real pro fisher
Dialogue: 100,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}简直是个钓鱼行家\N{\rENG}before the pole snapped.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.81,0:05:51.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谢谢\N{\rENG}Thanks.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:52.91,0:05:54.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}钓鱼确实扫兴了点\N{\rENG}So, fishing was a bust.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:54.51,0:05:56.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是我们还有其他的项目可以嗨\N{\rENG}But I-I got something that'll cheer you up.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:56.95,0:05:58.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}沙壶球\N{\rENG}Shuffleboard!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.68,0:05:59.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你怎么看\N{\rENG}What do you say?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:02.52,0:06:04.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}刚才怎么了\N{\rENG}What was that?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:06.16,0:06:07.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你没事吧\N{\rENG}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没事 怎么了\N{\rENG}Yeah. What's going on?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.56,0:06:11.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 你可以过来一下吗\N{\rENG}Steven!You got a moment?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:13.00,0:06:14.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}都没事吧 大副老爹\N{\rENG}Is everything okay,First Mate Dad?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘘 你听到了吗\N{\rENG}Shh!You hear that?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:16.90,0:06:19.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 没有\N{\rENG}Uhhh...no.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:19.04,0:06:20.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}船好像停下了\N{\rENG}I guess it stopped.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:20.37,0:06:21.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我想船应该是哪里坏了\N{\rENG}I think something's wrong with the boat.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:23.24,0:06:26.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊天哪 舵叶被卡住了\N{\rENG}Aw, geez, something's throwing off the rudder.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:26.28,0:06:27.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不知道现在是什么情况\N{\rENG}I don't know what's going on,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:27.61,0:06:30.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}使用指南也没有用\N{\rENG}and this owner's manual is no help.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:30.15,0:06:32.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那上面基本上是关于日光浴\N{\rENG}It's mostly advice on sun tanning
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.18,0:06:34.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还有鱼子酱要配什么饼干的建议\N{\rENG}and what crackers go with caviar.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:34.32,0:06:36.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那鱼子酱要配什么饼干?\N{\rENG}Well, what crackers go with caviar?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.39,0:06:38.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}水饼干\N{\rENG}Water crackers.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:42.76,0:06:44.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就是这个声音\N{\rENG}There it is.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:52.17,0:06:54.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}诶玛 我的引擎啊\N{\rENG}Oh, crud!The engine!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我可不懂怎么修引擎\N{\rENG}I don't know how to fix an engine.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这次旅程可能要多耽误一会儿了\N{\rENG}This trip might be a Little longer
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我的小伙计\N{\rENG}than we thought,little buddy.
Dialogue: 600,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.61,Hint,,0,0,0,,格雷格的话出自经典电视剧"Gilligan's Island"(格里甘岛),其中Skipper喜欢戴船长帽并称呼主角为little buddy
Dialogue: 100,0:07:03.48,0:07:04.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}青金石\N{\rENG}Lapis?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.52,0:07:08.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 我有些不那么好的消息\N{\rENG}Um...I have some not-so-good news.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:08.65,0:07:10.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}引擎出了问题\N{\rENG}There's trouble with the engine,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.26,0:07:12.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们可能要在海上困一阵子了\N{\rENG}and we might be stuck out here for a while.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.93,0:07:15.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我很抱歉\N{\rENG}I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.43,0:07:16.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这都是我的错\N{\rENG}This whole thing is my fault.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:16.36,0:07:20.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我只想让你开心 但是现在一切都搞砸了\N{\rENG}I just wanted you to have fun. but e-everything's a mess.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}早知道我不应该拉你来的\N{\rENG}I shouldn't have made you come on this trip.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:25.27,0:07:28.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是我的错 我才应该被怪罪\N{\rENG}It's my fault. I'm the one to blame.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:28.31,0:07:29.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不是的\N{\rENG}That's not true.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:29.67,0:07:31.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我真的努力试着享受这次旅行\N{\rENG}I'm really trying to enjoy it out here, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.44,0:07:34.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是我无法停止回忆融合成孔雀石的时候\N{\rENG}I can't stop thinking about being fused as Malachite,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:34.05,0:07:38.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是如何把她困在海底\N{\rENG}how I used all my strength to hold her down in the ocean,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:38.25,0:07:40.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}又是如何努力对抗铁石英\N{\rENG}and how I was always battling against Jasper
Dialogue: 100,0:07:40.45,0:07:41.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让她不能与我分开\N{\rENG}to keep her bound to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是现在不再是这样了\N{\rENG}But it's not like that anymore.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:44.02,0:07:46.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你不用和铁石英在一起了\N{\rENG}You don't have to be with Jasper.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:46.09,0:07:48.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那不是重点 我 --\N{\rENG}That's not it. I --
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.13,0:07:49.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我想她了\N{\rENG}I miss her.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.73,0:07:50.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啥?!\N{\rENG}What?!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:50.86,0:07:54.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们融合太久了\N{\rENG}We were fused for so long.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.10,0:07:56.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是...她很坏\N{\rENG}But...she's terrible.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:56.37,0:07:58.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我才是更坏的那个 我已经做了很多坏事\N{\rENG}I'm terrible! I did horrible things!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.67,0:08:01.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我-我弄断了你爸爸的腿 我盗走了你们地球上的海水\N{\rENG}I-I broke your dad's leg. I stole Earth's ocean!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:01.61,0:08:03.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}继续 继续反驳我啊\N{\rENG}Go on!Tell me I'm wrong!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.59,0:08:20.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}终于啊\N{\rENG}Finally!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:20.73,0:08:21.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}铁石英\N{\rENG}Jasper!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:21.73,0:08:24.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我还以为我再也赶不上你了\N{\rENG}I thought I'd never catch up to you!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.13,0:08:26.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你一直在跟踪我们?\N{\rENG}You've been following us?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.03,0:08:29.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我只是在跟踪你\N{\rENG}I've been following you.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:29.23,0:08:31.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}退后\N{\rENG}Stay back!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.07,0:08:37.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在你终于打算用盗版玫瑰的技能了?\N{\rENG}This dulled-down version of Rose Quartz works for you now?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.58,0:08:41.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你的盾不应该指向我\N{\rENG}You're pointing that shield the wrong way.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.78,0:08:44.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她才是你应该害怕的人\N{\rENG}She's the one you should be afraid of.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:44.18,0:08:45.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你说的不对\N{\rENG}That's not true.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.45,0:08:47.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你可骗不了我\N{\rENG}You can't lie to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:47.59,0:08:50.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我已经见识过你的力量了\N{\rENG}I've seen what you're capable of.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.26,0:08:52.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我以为我已经很残暴了 但是你 --\N{\rENG}I thought I was a brute, but you --
Dialogue: 100,0:08:52.99,0:08:55.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你简直是怪物\N{\rENG}you're a monster.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:55.89,0:08:57.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我...\N{\rENG}I...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:58.33,0:09:00.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}青金石不想再与你有任何瓜葛了\N{\rENG}Lapis doesn't want anything to do with you!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是我们...\N{\rENG}This is between...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:02.97,0:09:04.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}两个人之间的事!\N{\rENG}us!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:07.04,0:09:08.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文!\N{\rENG}Steven!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:10.94,0:09:12.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}请再次与我融合吧\N{\rENG}Let's be Malachite again.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:14.11,0:09:16.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么...你要这么做\N{\rENG}Why...would you want that?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:16.58,0:09:20.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我之前对融合的观念完全是错的 但是你让我理解了\N{\rENG}I was wrong about fusion. You made me understand!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:20.72,0:09:24.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}孔雀石比我们两个都更强 更大\N{\rENG}Malachite was bigger and stronger than both of us!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.32,0:09:25.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们能上天!\N{\rENG}We could fly!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:25.52,0:09:28.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}青金石 别听她的\N{\rENG}Lapis, don't listen to her!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.26,0:09:30.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}少管闲事!\N{\rENG}Stay out of this!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.06,0:09:31.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我之前对你很坏\N{\rENG}I was terrible to you.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:31.90,0:09:34.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我喜欢夺取你的一切\N{\rENG}I liked taking everything out on you.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:34.63,0:09:37.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是我必须这么做 我- 我讨厌你\N{\rENG}I needed to. I-I hated you.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:37.90,0:09:39.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们的融合太糟糕了\N{\rENG}It was bad!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.37,0:09:42.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这次不会再是那样了 我已经改变了\N{\rENG}It'll be better this time. I've changed.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.21,0:09:42.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你已经改变了我\N{\rENG}You've changed me.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.67,0:09:45.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}只有我才可以驾驭你这样的力量\N{\rENG}I'm the only one who can handle your kind of power.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:47.08,0:09:50.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们在一起将无人能挡\N{\rENG}Together,we'll be unstoppable!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:54.52,0:09:55.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我拒绝\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:55.69,0:09:56.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么\N{\rENG}What?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:56.62,0:09:57.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们这样的关系是不健康的\N{\rENG}What we had wasn't healthy.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.72,0:10:02.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我从来没喜欢过跟你在一起的感觉 我跟你再也不可能了\N{\rENG}I never want to feel like I felt with you -- never again!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.03,0:10:03.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你走吧\N{\rENG}So just go.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.93,0:10:06.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}-青金石 -她已经说拒绝了\N{\rENG}-Lapis! -She said, "No"!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不要纠缠她了\N{\rENG}Leave her alone!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.80,0:10:10.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这全是你的错\N{\rENG}This is your fault.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:10.33,0:10:12.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我要灭了你\N{\rENG}I'll shatter you!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.38,0:10:21.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}青金石 你做到了\N{\rENG}Lapis, you did it!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.38,0:10:23.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们俩没事吧\N{\rENG}Are you two okay?!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:23.05,0:10:24.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啥\N{\rENG}What?!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}刚才发生了啥\N{\rENG}What happened?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:28.55,0:10:31.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 说来话长\N{\rENG}Uh, it's kind of a long story.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:33.79,0:10:36.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我想最后我还是得买那船\N{\rENG}I guess I bought a boat after all.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:36.33,0:10:38.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 对不起 老爹\N{\rENG}Ehh, sorry, Dad.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.06,0:10:41.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不过 嘿 从这上面看海倒是挺美的\N{\rENG}But, hey, the ocean's really beautiful from up here.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是啊\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:43.97,0:10:46.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}确实\N{\rENG}It is.
